===Trivia===
[http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/H%26R_Block H&R-Block]'s [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/GIF GIF] image format was originally created to demonstrate the use of a program, though 
data is technically not software, "gifs" that demonstrate programs can be called demoware.